REMARK   3  C" CHAIN MAY HAVE EITHER THE SYN- OR ANTI- CONFORMATION. THE        
REMARK   3  DEPOSITED DATA HAVE ADENINE C7 IN THE ANTI- CONFORMATION.           
REMARK   3  INDEPENDENT REFINEMENTS OF THE STRUCTURAL MODEL WITH EITHER A       
REMARK   3  SYN- OR AN ANTI-CONFORMATION FOR THE 5'-TERMINAL ADENINE ((A7)      
REMARK   3  IN THE "C" CHAIN) YIELDED ELECTRON DENSITY MAPS WHICH GAVE NO       
REMARK   3  PREFERENCE FOR ONE CONFORMATION OVER THE OTHER, AND NO              
REMARK   3  INDICATION OF PARTIAL OCCUPANCIES FOR BOTH. THE INDEPENDENT         
REMARK   3  REFINEMENTS YIELDED THE SAME REFINEMENT STATISTICS. THE             
REMARK   3  DEPOSITED DATA CONTAIN THE ADENINE (A7) IN THE ANTI-                
REMARK   3  CONFORMATION. THE COORDINATES FOR THE SYN-ADENINE ARE               
